## Additional Information
To use the `@SessionScoped` annotation, you will need to add the `quarkus-undertow` extension to your `pom.xml` file. You can do this by adding the following dependency:

```xml
<dependency>
    <groupId>io.quarkus</groupId>
    <artifactId>quarkus-undertow</artifactId>
</dependency>
```

Additionally, you will need to import the `jakarta.enterprise.context.SessionScoped` annotation.
